Welcome to Gangster Paradise! You must read and agree to these Rules and Terms of Service before you login to the app. Any  updates / changes to the TOS will be clearly stated before you login to use the service.
This service is only for those aged 18+. If you are accessing the service via Apple iOS you may be 17+ due to credit restrictions. If you are found to be under age and using this service, you will be removed from the game and no refund of credits will be due.
RULE ROUNDUP
Please familiarize yourself with  all game rules before playing. Failure to be familiar with the game rules is not an excuse for breaking them and will not be accepted as a defence of your account.
We reserve the right to ban any user who is violating these rules or anything set out in this Terms of Service. Administrators are allowed to access your account for security/investigation, or other purposes that they feel appropriate. We will not read any private communications unless given permission to do so.
You
MUST NOT:
Profit or gain any advantage through the use of multiple accounts.
Play the game unless you are eighteen (18+) in age or older.
Sell or give away your account to any other player.
Access or otherwise attempt to infiltrate (crack/hack) anyone else's account other than your own.
Use any kind of program/script which automatically does actions or automates any other game activities.
Exploit a bug in the game to make money, gain properties, and or make harms to any other players, or to the game itself.
Bugs include unforeseen loopholes which give you an unfair advantage over other players. All such bugs must be reported help desk available within the help area of the game.
Abuse, bully or harass other players in the communication area. Repeated violations of this rule will result in a permanent ban to your account.
Despite this, the theme and age rating of the game mean you should expect some belittling play and talk. Facilities are available to block and hide any unwanted communication.
Intentionally spam or flood the forum, chat room, or other communication methods.
Advertise any other website/product or any other material.
Please remember:
Users are ONLY allowed to access their own account. Sharing of accounts is not allowed. Logging on to someone else's account is not allowed. Anyone caught on someone else's account is subject to the banning of all linked accounts on the device and/or IP address at the sole discretion of the Administrator.
Players are fully responsible for what they do with their character names and passwords, we are not responsible for your passwords, and they are encrypted (cannot be read) safely in the database which no one except for Administrators can access.
If a user’s account gets hacked or accessed       by another player, GP is not responsible for the undoing of any results of       said hacking. This includes the return of any Money, Credits, Cars,       Properties and any other goods of GP, as well as, the un-banning of the account. Once reported, Administrators or Moderators may investigate and ban any users involved in said hacking.
Accounts       that have been banned for any reason lose all rights to any Money,       Credits, Cars, Properties or any other game possessions remaining on the       account.
