You  agree to not use the Service to:
1.  Upload, post, email, transmit or otherwise make available any Content that is  unlawful, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, tortuous, defamatory,  vulgar, obscene, libellous, invasive of another's privacy, hateful, or  racially, ethnically or otherwise objectionable. When a user is reported doing  so appropriate measures will be taken. Verbally abusing players and staff is  considered poor etiquette and measures can be taken without notice or  explanation;
2.  Harm minors in any way;
3.  Impersonate any person or entity, including, but not limited to, a Gangster  Paradise administrator, forum leader, guide or host, or falsely state or  otherwise misrepresent your affiliation with a person or entity;
4.  Upload, post, email, transmit or otherwise make available any unsolicited or  unauthorized advertising, promotional materials, "junk mail,"  "spam," "chain letters," "pyramid schemes," or  any other form of solicitation.
5.  Upload, post, email, transmit or otherwise make available any material that  contains software viruses or any other computer code, files or programs  designed to interrupt, destroy or limit the functionality of any computer  software or hardware or telecommunications equipment;
6.  Interfere with or disrupt the Service or servers or networks connected to the  Service, or disobey any requirements, procedures, policies or regulations of  networks connected to the Service;
7.  "Stalk" or otherwise harass another; or
8.  Collect or store personal data about other users.
9.  Errors in the system (this is the game and hardware) to benefit from it, it is  considered as cheating. All bugs should be reported to an administrator as soon  as discovered;
You  acknowledge that Gangster Paradise does not pre-screen Content, but that Gangster  Paradise and its designees shall have the right (but not the obligation) in their  sole discretion to refuse or move any Content that is available via the  Service. Without limiting the foregoing, Gangster Paradise and its designees  shall have the right to remove any Content that violates the TOS or is  otherwise objectionable. You agree that you must evaluate, and bear all risks  associated with, the use of any Content, including any reliance on the  accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of such Content. In this regard, you  acknowledge that you may not rely on any Content created by Gangster Paradise  or submitted to Gangster Paradise, including without limitation information in Gangster  Paradise's forums and in all other parts of the Service.
