Credits may be purchased by users using the information provided within the "Credits" section of the app. This is optional and not a requirement or hidden cost. You must understand that payments are processed by our service provider
Fortumo
who can be contacted
here
. Any problem with a purchase should be brought to their attention. Any possible problems you experience before or after a purchase should be submitted to our ticket based support system (GP Support) under the "Credit Purchase Problem" category to be sent to the correct personnel. Upon following the instructions given in the Credits section of Gangster Paradise OR / AND additional methods of payments on the affiliated Fortumo website, a user will be provided with a password delivered from the Fortumo system. Fortumo will automatically post the password and purchase data to the Gangster Paradise database, allowing a user to enter the password provided into the Credits section and receive their in-game credits. This password can only be entered once by one user. Purchases are non-subscription based.
Credits are not required to use the service, however they provide additional virtual items, advancements or features that may benefit a user and enhance their experience. Due to the optional nature of the credits system, in a normal hourly session a user could use anywhere between 0 to around 100 credits, this being entirely dependent on if they've already purchased some of the in-game items available or are in need of the benefits at the time.
You agree that Gangster Paradise is only responsible for  providing adequate credits to the customer after a purchase. After a customer  receives his or her purchased credits, he/she is to be held fully responsible  for what is to become of the credits. You agree that Gangster Paradise will be  in no way responsible for (but is not limited to) the loss of credits due to  unauthorized access to your account.
Credits work on a no refund, no return policy. After the credits have been added to your account on the game you cannot claim a refund or return the credits for your money back. You are responsible for their safety.
You agree to not (re)sell Gangster Paradise credits for anything other than  in-game goods. Selling credits (regardless of how you received them) for real  money is prohibited, and will not be tolerated. You agree not to transfer credits  which will ultimately lead to you receiving real currency. You agree not to  purchase credits with real money from users other than those who officially  sell them.
You agree (and understand) that after a reset, you can claim 100% of your paid  for credits
IF
and only if you purchased them within 1 month of the  reset. In other words, your credits will only "roll over" to the next  round if a reset occurred within 1 month of purchasing your credits. After  that, they cannot be claimed.
We hope  you have fun playing the game
